{"tid":1223250,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"譚惠珠梁愛詩無回應應否暫緩或撤回修訂《逃犯條例》","createTime":"2019-06-14T16:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T16:00:53.000Z","uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc46ee00ba1d8651af79c7f439b855019cf9c8b7","tid":1223250,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"譚惠珠梁愛詩無回應應否暫緩或撤回修訂《逃犯條例》<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠和前主任梁愛詩出席一個活動後，被多次追問特區政府應否暫緩或撤回修訂《逃犯條例》、金鐘警民衝突是否暴動等，譚惠珠說，今日沒有看新聞，梁愛詩就說，一句也不會回應。<br />\n<br />\n出席同一個場合的立法會前主席曾鈺成，被問到有關問題時，亦沒有回應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462923-20190614.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462923-20190614.htm&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8IHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=ce6bd7bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462923-20190614.htm&h=01572040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462923-20190614.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩係金鐘俾人屌完應該驚咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}